ABOUT US

Infinity Building Technology is a Canberra based manufacturer of prefabricated steel wall frames, floor joists and roof trusses for both commercial and residential building use.

Our Group

The Infinity Building Tech is a facility with cutting-edge production equipment, expert management, and a safe training atmosphere. We give you with first-class service, with 0% defects as our goal, in addition to our exceptional corporate environment. Our commitment to you is a better factory with better products for our consumers.

Our Manufacturing Facility

We now have a contemporary production workshop and a new huge processing centre. This is to verify that the manufacturing equipment is accurate, adheres to all technical specifications, and maintains the highest level of quality control throughout the production process.

We supply all you need to ensure that your home is built with strength, durability and accuracy.

There is no need for cutting, welding, or hard lifting.

Steel does not absorb moisture, thus there are no weather delays.

Accuracy in construction means that windows, doors, and bathrooms fit perfectly the first time.

To erect on-site, just simple tools are necessary - construction is completed quickly.
